 294:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2c.c ****      [..]
 295:Drivers/STM32F4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32f4xx_hal_i2c.c ****        (@) You can refer to the I2C HAL driver header file for more useful macros
